90
00:04:19,769 --> 00:04:23,710
And then volunteers on motorcycles come to
rescue them.

91
00:04:23,710 --> 00:04:26,849
Yes, times are so desperate in Hong Kong,

92
00:04:26,849 --> 00:04:31,090
