109
00:05:16,469 --> 00:05:19,229
If we have to respond,

110
00:05:19,229 --> 00:05:28,190
I believe the only option is to use deadly
weapons.”

111
00:05:28,190 --> 00:05:30,770
So once again, Hong Kong police are threatening

112
00:05:30,770 --> 00:05:34,150
to use deadly weapons on Hong Kong protesters.

113
00:05:34,150 --> 00:05:36,210
Which is no empty threat,

114
00:05:36,210 --> 00:05:37,479
